http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/title.value: South Carolina Academic Standards for Health and Safety Education

http://purl.org/dc/terms/description.value: The academic standards describe what students should know and be able to do. Each of the eight standards is demonstrated with performance indicators at each grade level. Standard 1 in this document is the traditional content and knowledge standard. Standards 2 through 8 have skill emphasis.
